A good way to contribute patches is to attach them to issues in the 
project JIRA issue tracker:

   http://webteam.archive.org/jira

There's already an issue about the fact a number of DecideRules are 
missing the necessary addKeys() initializers. See:

http://webteam.archive.org/jira/browse/HER-1593

For other patches and contributions, you can open new issues, if an 
appropriate one does not already exist.

Thanks for finding and fixing bugs!

- Gordon @ IA
